&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; &lt;span class="nb"&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s2"&gt;&amp;#34;The malicious process &amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="nv"&gt;$MALICIOUS_PROCESS&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="s2"&gt;&amp;#39; must be stopped.&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; &lt;span class="nb"&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s2"&gt;&amp;#34;➡️ Run this command to stop it:&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
