&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="line"&gt;&lt;span class="cl"&gt; &lt;span class="nb"&gt;echo&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="s2"&gt;&amp;#34;🔒 After taking the steps above, it is strongly recommended to check for persistence mechanisms and change critical passwords.&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
